title: Biosfera Nature
description: Several locations in Siena. The front of this store looks like a pharmacy with vitamins, but the store also sells fresh fruits. Stocks many kinds of cereal, grains, flour, has agave syrup and the usual health food stuff. Further in the back of the store is a chilled vegan section with soya yoghurt, dairy free ice cream, tofu and seitan products, and some frozen meat-like vegan foods.
